---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About - Upsilon Hub"
  description="Learn about Upsilon Hub's mission to track breakthroughs in Quantum Physics, Astrophysics, and High Energy Physics using automated intelligence."
>

  <section class="relative overflow-hidden border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 mb-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 md:py-24 relative z-10">
      <p class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-primary-light dark:text-primary-dark mb-4">About the platform</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-text-light dark:text-text-dark tracking-tighter leading-[1.05] mb-6">
        Upsilon<span class="text-primary-light dark:text-primary-dark">.</span>Hub
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 max-w-xl leading-relaxed">
        An automated intelligence platform tracking the frontier of modern physics.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.03] dark:opacity-[0.06]" style="background-image: linear-gradient(currentColor 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, currentColor 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 40px 40px;"></div>
  </section>

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 pb-24 space-y-20">

    <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-px bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">
      {[
        { value: "15", label: "Curated Sources" },
        { value: "150+", label: "Articles Daily" },
        { value: "10", label: "Physics Topics" },
      ].map(stat => (
        <div class="bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark px-6 py-8 text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-primary-light dark:text-primary-dark mb-1">{stat.value}</div>
          <div class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-600">{stat.label}</div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[1fr_2fr] gap-12 items-start">
      <div>
        <p class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-primary-light dark:text-primary-dark mb-3">Purpose</p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-text-light dark:text-text-dark tracking-tight">The Mission</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-base md:text-[17px]">
        <p>
          Keeping up with scientific breakthroughs is difficult. The <strong class="text-text-light dark:text-text-dark">signal-to-noise ratio</strong> in modern media is low, and important discoveries often get buried under clickbait.
        </p>
        <p>
          Upsilon.Hub solves this by aggregating raw, high-impact research news from the world's most respected institutions like <strong class="text-text-light dark:text-text-dark">CERN, NASA, MIT</strong>, and leading physics journals, into one clean, real-time feed. Each article is paired with an AI-generated summary written for curious readers, with a direct link to the original source for those who want the full story.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="mb-10">
        <p class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-primary-light dark:text-primary-dark mb-3">Under the hood</p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-text-light dark:text-text-dark tracking-tight">How It Works</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">

        <div class="group rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 p-6 bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark hover:border-primary-light dark:hover:border-primary-dark transition-colors duration-200">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-primary-light/10 dark:bg-primary-dark/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-light dark:text-primary-dark" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <strong class="text-text-light dark:text-text-dark font-bold block mb-2">Automated Retrieval</strong>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">A custom aggregation engine runs daily via GitHub Actions, pulling from 15 curated RSS feeds across physics and science media.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="group rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 p-6 bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark hover:border-primary-light dark:hover:border-primary-dark transition-colors duration-200">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-primary-light/10 dark:bg-primary-dark/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-light dark:text-primary-dark" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 4a1 1 0 011-1h16a1 1 0 011 1v2a1 1 0 01-.293.707L13 13.414V19a1 1 0 01-.553.894l-4 2A1 1 0 017 21v-7.586L3.293 6.707A1 1 0 013 6V4z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <strong class="text-text-light dark:text-text-dark font-bold block mb-2">Smart Filtering</strong>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Algorithms filter out irrelevant noise and classify articles into physics categories : Quantum, Astrophysics, High Energy, Nanotech, and more.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="group rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 p-6 bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark hover:border-primary-light dark:hover:border-primary-dark transition-colors duration-200">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-primary-light/10 dark:bg-primary-dark/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-light dark:text-primary-dark" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <strong class="text-text-light dark:text-text-dark font-bold block mb-2">AI Summaries</strong>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Each article is summarized by Google Gemini : clear, accessible, and written for curious readers. The original source is always one click away.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="group rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 p-6 bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark hover:border-primary-light dark:hover:border-primary-dark transition-colors duration-200">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-primary-light/10 dark:bg-primary-dark/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-light dark:text-primary-dark" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 16a4 4 0 01-.88-7.903A5 5 0 1115.9 6L16 6a5 5 0 011 9.9M15 13l-3-3m0 0l-3 3m3-3v12"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <strong class="text-text-light dark:text-text-dark font-bold block mb-2">Self-Deploying</strong>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">The system automatically rebuilds and deploys the live site on Vercel whenever new data is ready.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 p-6 md:p-8 flex gap-5 items-start">
      <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-primary-light/10 dark:bg-primary-dark/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-light dark:text-primary-dark" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-base font-bold text-text-light dark:text-text-dark mb-2">Privacy &amp; Copyright</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
          Upsilon Hub only uses the excerpts that publishers voluntarily distribute via RSS feeds. No full article text is reproduced. AI summaries are original derivative works. No user data is collected or stored.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 pt-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-text-light dark:text-text-dark tracking-tight mb-3">Have Feedback or Suggestions?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8">
        Feel free to reach out for collaboration, bug reports, or just to say hi.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center items-center gap-4">
        <a
          href="https://t.me/ScooperTrooper_WitzchelStein"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="w-full sm:w-auto inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-[#229ED9] hover:bg-[#1f8eb3] text-white font-bold rounded-lg transition-colors text-sm"
        >
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M11.944 0A12 12 0 0 0 0 12a12 12 0 0 0 12 12 12 12 0 0 0 12-12A12 12 0 0 0 11.944 0zm4.962 7.224c.1-.002.321.023.465.14a.506.506 0 0 1 .171.325c.016.093.036.306.02.472-.18 1.898-.962 6.502-1.36 8.627-.168.9-.499 1.201-.82 1.23-.696.065-1.225-.46-1.9-.902-1.056-.693-1.653-1.124-2.678-1.8-1.185-.78-.417-1.21.258-1.91.177-.184 3.247-2.977 3.307-3.23.007-.032.014-.15-.056-.212s-.174-.041-.249-.024c-.106.024-1.793 1.14-5.061 3.345-.48.33-.913.49-1.302.48-.428-.008-1.252-.241-1.865-.44-.752-.245-1.349-.374-1.297-.789.027-.216.325-.437.893-.663 3.498-1.524 5.83-2.529 6.998-3.014 3.332-1.386 4.025-1.627 4.476-1.638z"/></svg>
          Telegram
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</Layout>